OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Flargely clear evening and night, with
OL,7,Fwinds gradually easing, allowing
OL,8,Ftemperatures to fall more sharply
OL,9,Fovernight and feel much cooler than
OL,10,Frecently. Cloud will spread in from
OL,11,Fthe west by morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FDry but increasingly cloudy
OL,14,Fthrough the morning. Some sunshine
OL,15,Fwill break through later, especially
OL,16,Fin the east where it'll be more
OL,17,Fprolonged. Overnight, outbreaks of
OL,18,Flight rain will spread eastwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
